1
00:00:20,180 --> 00:00:26,020
=Manbo Destiny=

2
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:27,980
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:31,561
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

4
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:37,881
Song Pai, Lin Ge.

5
00:00:39,727 --> 00:00:41,250
Regarding this disaster relief effort,

6
00:00:41,266 --> 00:00:43,112
you both performed exceptionally well.

7
00:00:44,035 --> 00:00:46,458
I intend to reward you properly.

8
00:00:49,804 --> 00:00:50,420
Your Majesty,

9
00:00:51,150 --> 00:00:52,374
we have already discussed this.

10
00:00:53,489 --> 00:00:54,720
If a reward must be given,

11
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:57,489
please grant it
to the disaster-stricken citizens.

12
00:00:58,374 --> 00:01:00,720
They still need much support
for reconstruction.

13
00:01:01,835 --> 00:01:02,527
Your Majesty,

14
00:01:03,374 --> 00:01:05,104
we will also help the victims afterward

15
00:01:05,104 --> 00:01:06,643
by expanding e-commerce initiatives,

16
00:01:07,374 --> 00:01:09,451
connecting them with buyers in China,

17
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:12,412
and helping them rebuild
their homes as soon as possible.

18
00:01:13,297 --> 00:01:14,104
Very well.

19
00:01:15,874 --> 00:01:17,258
This truly reflects royal dignity.

20
00:01:19,247 --> 00:01:22,208
You two care deeply
for the nation and its people.

21
00:01:22,208 --> 00:01:24,939
I am greatly comforted by this.

22
00:01:28,016 --> 00:01:28,901
Recently,

23
00:01:30,016 --> 00:01:32,093
I have been feeling unwell.

24
00:01:32,824 --> 00:01:35,477
Moreover, affairs of state

25
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:37,093
have become increasingly demanding.

26
00:01:37,939 --> 00:01:42,093
Therefore, I must choose one of you

27
00:01:42,093 --> 00:01:44,247
to serve as Regent,

28
00:01:44,824 --> 00:01:46,670
to assist me in governing the country.

29
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,463
Your Majesty,

30
00:01:51,117 --> 00:01:52,963
the First Prince
is virtuous and capable.

31
00:01:52,963 --> 00:01:55,117
His appointment would
be a blessing to the nation.

32
00:01:56,309 --> 00:01:57,578
Your Majesty,

33
00:01:57,886 --> 00:02:00,309
the First Prince is deeply loved
by the people.

34
00:02:00,309 --> 00:02:02,386
He is the best candidate for Regent.

35
00:02:03,617 --> 00:02:04,347
Father,

36
00:02:04,578 --> 00:02:07,347
I also believe Song Pai
is the best choice.

37
00:02:16,347 --> 00:02:18,232
I agreed to withdraw
from the succession,

38
00:02:20,001 --> 00:02:21,540
but remember this,

39
00:02:21,847 --> 00:02:24,347
if you dare lay a finger
on Guan Mengmeng,

40
00:02:24,347 --> 00:02:26,117
I will never let you off.

41
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,928
Your Majesty,

42
00:02:32,697 --> 00:02:33,466
I disagree.

43
00:02:34,582 --> 00:02:36,466
Song Pai, what are you doing?

44
00:02:40,801 --> 00:02:41,724
Song Pai.

45
00:02:42,801 --> 00:02:44,685
Are you facing some difficulty?

46
00:02:45,724 --> 00:02:47,532
The matter of regency is no small issue.

47
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:48,900
It concerns the fate of the nation.

48
00:02:50,916 --> 00:02:52,262
My experience is still limited.

49
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,224
I wish to think it over further.

50
00:02:55,724 --> 00:02:57,185
This matter cannot be forced.

51
00:02:58,416 --> 00:03:00,109
You may take time to consider it.

52
00:03:11,409 --> 00:03:13,025
Song Pai, what's wrong?

53
00:03:13,294 --> 00:03:14,602
Did something happen?

54
00:03:15,063 --> 00:03:16,486
This is such a great opportunity.

55
00:03:16,755 --> 00:03:17,371
I know.

56
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,608
I just want to be more fully prepared.

57
00:03:43,085 --> 00:03:44,238
(The contract must be here.)

58
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:46,200
(I must find it as soon as possible.)

59
00:04:59,431 --> 00:05:02,585
(So this is the First Prince
who breaks his word.)

60
00:05:19,089 --> 00:05:19,820
Wen Shanna.

61
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:21,551
Wen Shanna.

62
00:05:22,512 --> 00:05:24,012
Why are you here so late?

63
00:05:24,012 --> 00:05:25,705
What happened tonight must not be told.

64
00:05:25,705 --> 00:05:26,950
Especially not to Guan Mengmeng.

65
00:05:33,243 --> 00:05:35,089
Coming to my house so late,

66
00:05:35,897 --> 00:05:37,551
is it because of my father?

67
00:05:50,527 --> 00:05:51,280
What are you doing?

68
00:05:52,142 --> 00:05:54,488
Help! Someone help!

69
00:05:55,681 --> 00:05:56,873
Help!

70
00:05:57,681 --> 00:05:58,373
Help!

71
00:05:58,373 --> 00:05:58,835
Go!

72
00:05:59,988 --> 00:06:00,790
What are you doing?

73
00:06:04,104 --> 00:06:04,796
Mengmeng!

74
00:06:20,642 --> 00:06:21,835
None of you will touch her!

75
00:06:26,373 --> 00:06:27,104
Song Pai!

76
00:06:30,219 --> 00:06:31,142
You're injured!

77
00:06:31,373 --> 00:06:32,027
Song Pai!

78
00:06:32,565 --> 00:06:33,642
Why are you so foolish?

79
00:06:34,104 --> 00:06:34,719
Song Pai!

80
00:06:35,681 --> 00:06:36,335
Song Pai!

81
00:06:37,027 --> 00:06:37,642
Song Pai.

82
00:06:38,488 --> 00:06:42,950
Only if you withdraw from the succession
can Guan Mengmeng secure her future.

83
00:06:43,642 --> 00:06:45,296
Otherwise, her fate...

84
00:06:47,527 --> 00:06:48,335
I'm fine.

85
00:06:48,835 --> 00:06:49,758
I'm fine. Really.

86
00:06:49,758 --> 00:06:50,790
As long as you're alright.

87
00:06:52,604 --> 00:06:53,181
Song Pai.

88
00:06:53,412 --> 00:06:53,988
Boss.

89
00:06:55,335 --> 00:06:56,296
Song Pai!

90
00:06:56,681 --> 00:06:57,565
Song Pai!

91
00:07:12,604 --> 00:07:15,258
Why won't you become Regent?

92
00:07:17,988 --> 00:07:18,873
Father,

93
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,280
I am unworthy of such
a heavy responsibility.

94
00:07:23,488 --> 00:07:24,719
I humbly ask you,

95
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:26,873
from this day forward,

96
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:29,390
to allow me to withdraw
from the succession.

97
00:07:32,488 --> 00:07:33,373
Song Pai.

98
00:07:35,104 --> 00:07:37,565
You have greatly disappointed me.

99
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:50,604
Pai, why did you withdraw
from the succession?

100
00:07:50,604 --> 00:07:52,181
Lin Ge, calm down.

101
00:07:52,181 --> 00:07:53,258
Nana, don't stop me.

102
00:07:53,719 --> 00:07:55,258
I have to get answers from my brother.

103
00:07:55,565 --> 00:07:57,027
You could have become Regent.

104
00:07:58,527 --> 00:07:59,835
Wouldn't that have been great?

105
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,719
I withdrew.

106
00:08:02,650 --> 00:08:04,330
Then neither of us needs
to argue anymore.

107
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:05,681
What are you talking about?

108
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:07,450
What I want is fairness.

109
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,380
What do you call what you're doing now?

110
00:08:13,681 --> 00:08:15,610
I'm no longer suitable
to compete for the throne.

111
00:08:16,296 --> 00:08:19,488
Manbo Kingdom needs a king
who can truly benefit the people.

112
00:08:21,681 --> 00:08:23,104
I believe you can do it.

113
00:08:26,406 --> 00:08:27,522
You say you're not suitable?

114
00:08:29,406 --> 00:08:31,200
You were trained
from childhood to be king.

115
00:08:31,210 --> 00:08:32,290
What kind of excuse is that?

116
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:36,592
Song Pai.

117
00:08:39,092 --> 00:08:40,208
What on earth happened?

118
00:08:45,377 --> 00:08:47,069
Your father took the contract.

119
00:08:47,915 --> 00:08:48,839
The contract?

120
00:08:50,415 --> 00:08:51,954
I burned it with my own hands.

121
00:08:53,031 --> 00:08:54,069
Could it be my father

122
00:08:54,069 --> 00:08:55,146
switch the contract?

123
00:08:56,031 --> 00:08:56,800
The contract?

124
00:08:57,992 --> 00:08:58,800
What contract?

125
00:08:59,646 --> 00:09:00,723
What are you talking about?

126
00:09:01,915 --> 00:09:03,108
Saul forced me.

127
00:09:04,685 --> 00:09:07,415
These past few days
I tried hard to get it back,

128
00:09:07,415 --> 00:09:08,762
but I still failed.

129
00:09:11,723 --> 00:09:12,992
Why would my father do that?

130
00:09:14,377 --> 00:09:15,492
I need to ask him myself.

131
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,531
Pai, what is really going on?

132
00:09:22,031 --> 00:09:23,454
Tell me, quickly.

133
00:09:26,915 --> 00:09:29,108
Father, why did you hit me?

134
00:09:29,608 --> 00:09:30,723
Why did I hit you?

135
00:09:32,531 --> 00:09:34,531
You secretly burned the contract,

136
00:09:35,262 --> 00:09:37,531
trying to cut ties with the Queen.

137
00:09:37,531 --> 00:09:38,954
I haven't even punished you yet,

138
00:09:38,954 --> 00:09:40,646
and you dare question me?

139
00:09:41,454 --> 00:09:41,954
Father.

140
00:09:42,608 --> 00:09:43,915
The Queen is unreliable.

141
00:09:44,069 --> 00:09:46,839
I heard her say she could abandon
our family at any time.

142
00:09:46,839 --> 00:09:47,569
Impossible!

143
00:09:50,415 --> 00:09:51,454
The Queen's faction

144
00:09:52,262 --> 00:09:53,415
and our family

145
00:09:55,108 --> 00:09:56,377
are both conservatives.

146
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,877
We've cooperated for years.

147
00:09:58,608 --> 00:10:00,146
Our interests are deeply entangled.

148
00:10:00,454 --> 00:10:01,839
We can never be separated.

149
00:10:04,185 --> 00:10:07,877
You must formally apologize
to the Queen.

150
00:10:08,146 --> 00:10:08,954
Father.

151
00:10:08,954 --> 00:10:09,492
Silence!

152
00:10:11,377 --> 00:10:12,685
Reflect on this properly.

153
00:10:20,685 --> 00:10:22,608
Son, have some fruit.

154
00:10:23,454 --> 00:10:24,185
Thank you.

155
00:10:26,646 --> 00:10:27,992
How is your elder brother?

156
00:10:29,223 --> 00:10:30,108
Not very well.

157
00:10:30,569 --> 00:10:31,790
His injuries are quite serious.

158
00:10:33,108 --> 00:10:35,723
I know you're very close
to your brother.

159
00:10:36,262 --> 00:10:38,723
Seeing him hurt pains me too.

160
00:10:39,685 --> 00:10:41,646
But since things have come to this,

161
00:10:42,569 --> 00:10:44,300
it's time for you
to shoulder everything.

162
00:10:44,569 --> 00:10:45,031
Mother.

163
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:45,800
I...

164
00:10:46,031 --> 00:10:47,800
While Song Pai is recovering,

165
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,108
you should take responsibility

166
00:10:49,108 --> 00:10:50,954
and serve as Regent
to manage state affairs.

167
00:10:51,915 --> 00:10:53,031
Once he recovers,

168
00:10:53,223 --> 00:10:54,877
everything will transition naturally.

169
00:10:55,377 --> 00:10:58,146
Your elder brother will thank you then.

170
00:11:00,262 --> 00:11:00,954
Alright.

171
00:11:01,839 --> 00:11:03,069
Then until my brother recovers,

172
00:11:03,646 --> 00:11:05,108
I'll serve as Regent in his place.

173
00:11:06,954 --> 00:11:08,646
That's my good son.

174
00:11:13,954 --> 00:11:14,800
Go on.

175
00:11:15,377 --> 00:11:18,146
Become the most dazzling prince
of this nation.

176
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:01,985
(Mengmeng.)

177
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:04,061
(I will find every way to protect you.)

178
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,792
(No matter what happens,)

179
00:12:06,215 --> 00:12:08,369
(I won't let anyone hurt you.)

180
00:12:08,946 --> 00:12:09,523
(I hope)

181
00:12:10,446 --> 00:12:11,869
(that we can always be together,)

182
00:12:12,792 --> 00:12:14,100
(never to be separated.)

183
00:13:25,638 --> 00:13:26,331
Mengmeng.

184
00:13:31,292 --> 00:13:32,138
Mengmeng.

185
00:13:41,677 --> 00:13:42,754
Mengmeng.

186
00:13:52,831 --> 00:13:53,715
(Song Pai.)

187
00:13:53,792 --> 00:13:55,292
(From today onward,)

188
00:13:55,292 --> 00:13:57,523
(our contract relationship
is terminated.)

189
00:13:57,523 --> 00:14:00,254
(I will return the money
you transferred to me.)

190
00:14:00,754 --> 00:14:01,561
(Guan Mengmeng.)

191
00:14:02,446 --> 00:14:03,100
What's going on?

192
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:08,190
You think you can run
after sleeping with me?

193
00:14:08,677 --> 00:14:09,638
Not that easy.

194
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:21,940
♪I do this for you♪

195
00:14:22,340 --> 00:14:24,580
♪The love is fake♪

196
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:27,340
♪The love is true♪

197
00:14:28,140 --> 00:14:30,220
♪For you♪
